page.title: 12 HOBBIES
page.content:
My hobby is swimming.I go to the baths a lot.I can do the breast stroke and the back stroke but I'm no good at the crawl.I have passed my elementary test and my proficiency test.For my elementary I had to do a length any stroke.For my proficiency I had to do a neat dive from the side of the pool and four lengths of any stroke.I used to go to the baths every Sunday morning with my dad but now I don't because it doesn't open any more on a Sunday.For swimming you take your clothes off and put on a fancy costume which is a specially for swimming. Swimming is a way of transporting your self through water.You swim for leisure and it's fun.
Suzanne Mowatt
